        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "*Sinister knight* armor shrouds the wearer\u2019s identity in secrecy, allowing Crimson Reclaimers to pass among foes without being immediately unmasked. The wearer gains a +1 item bonus to Deception checks.",
